          "returnType": null,
          "description": "Raw wall-clock delta between this frame and the previous one, in milliseconds. May exceed the clamped simulation delta when the engine's internal MAX_DELTA_MS guard activates (e.g. after a debugger pause or device sleep/resume). Use this for profiling to distinguish actual elapsed time from the clamped simulation delta passed to update recipients."
